    .container.sm
      p.title About the Project
      p Jobstar is a job board with the list of job opportunities depending on your field of interest. It also has a section of videos and curated lists of blogs that will help users to educate themselves in getting a job. 
      
    .img-block-long.mb-50
      img.img-fluid(src="assets/img/jobstar/overview.png", alt="")
    
